tting%20older%20changed%20her%20dating%20life%20in%20an%20unexpected%20way.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20she%20dated%20older%20men%20in%20her%2020s%20and%2030s%2C%20she%20said%20turning%2040%20led%20her%20to%20date%20younger%20men.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20now%20I'm%20heading%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20because%20I'm%20too%20hot%20to%20be%20dating%20a%2065-year-old%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchelsea-handler-parenting-classes-despite-not-having-kids-children-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChelsea%20Handler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2051%2C%20isn't%20sticking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-sunday-newsletter-dating-rules-are-changing-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraditional%20dating%3C%2Fa%3E%20expectations%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday's%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQObgTDZUMuM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIRL%20podcast%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20the%20comedian%20spoke%20about%20dating%20and%20the%20reason%20she%20doesn't%20want%20to%20build%20her%20life%20around%20a%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHandler%20told%20host%20Angie%20Martinez%20that%20she's%20seeing%20a%20man%2014%20years%20her%20junior%2C%20whom%20she%20met%20at%20a%20casino%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-avoid-las-vegas-reccomendations-frequent-visitor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELas%20Vegas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20asked%20about%20their%20age%20gap%2C%20Handler%20said%20she%20doesn't%20%26quot%3Breally%20feel%20anything%26quot%3B%20about%20it%2C%20but%20added%20that%20she%20initially%20wasn't%20looking%20to%20date%20someone%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20young%2C%2020s%2C%2030s%2C%20I%20always%20dated%20older%20guys.%2020s%2C%20like%2020%20years%20older%20than%20me.%20I%20always%20dated%2040-year-olds%20when%20I%20was%2020%2C%2050-year-olds%20when%20I%20was%2030%2C%26quot%3B%20Handler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20she%20turned%2040%2C%20she%20began%20rethinking%20that%20pattern%2C%20and%20decided%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20date%2060-year-olds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%2C%20I've%20got%20to%20flip%20it%20and%20reverse%20it%2C%20you%20know%3F%20So%2C%20now%20I'm%20heading%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20because%20I'm%20too%20hot%20to%20be%20dating%20a%2065-year-old.%20Let's%20be%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20Handler%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20I%20don't%20work%20this%20hard%20on%20myself%20and%20take%20such%20good%20care%20of%20myself%20so%20that%20I%20can't%20have%20fun%20and%2C%20you%20know%2C%20have%20a%20good%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20once%20she%20got%20to%20know%20the%20man%20she's%20been%20seeing%20better%2C%20that%20%26quot%3Bage%20thing%20went%20out%20the%20window.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Handler%20said%20she%20values%20her%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20traveling%20a%20lot.%20I%20like%20hooking%20up%20with%20guys.%20I%20don't%20like%20to%20get%20too%20serious.%20I%20don't%20want%20someone%20in%20my%20space%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20her%20%26quot%3Bwhole%20vibe%26quot%3B%20is%20about%20freedom.%20Even%20though%20she%20sees%20marriage%20as%20%26quot%3Boutdated%2C%26quot%3B%20Handler%20said%20she'd%20do%20it%20for%20the%20irony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20you%20know%2C%20since%20I've%20bemoaned%20marriage%20my%20whole%20entire%20public%20life%2C%20I%20would%20be%20really%20hypocritical%20for%20me%20to%20get%20married%2C%20which%20means%20I'll%20probably%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Handler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHandler%20has%20long%20been%20candid%20about%20her%20approach%20to%20dating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2DGzjYtuMYY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECall%20Her%20Daddy%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20February%202025%2C%20Handler%20said%20she%20prefers%20to%20live%20life%20on%20her%20own%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20interested%20in%20long-term%20commitments%2C%20to%20work%2C%20to%20people%2C%20to%20anything.%20I%20am%20a%20free%20spirit%20and%20I%20want%20to%20remain%20and%20soar%20like%20an%20eagle%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20host%20Alex%20Cooper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20isn't%20the%20only%20Hollywood%20star%20who%20has%20embraced%20relationships%20with%20younger%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Cher%20said%20she%20prefers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcher-dates-younger-men-older-dead-terrified-age-gap-relationship-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edate%20younger%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20older%20ones%20are%20often%20intimidated%20by%20her.%20The%20singer%20has%20a%2040-year%20age%20gap%20with%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20Alexander%20Edwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftracee-ellis-ross-prefers-dating-younger-men-age-gap-relationship-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETracee%20Ellis%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20she%20dates%20younger%20men%20because%20men%20her%20age%20are%20often%20%26quot%3Bsteeped%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-ways-toxic-masculinity-shows-up-in-your-relationship-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etoxic%20masculinity.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20anything%20that%20starts%20to%20smell%20of%20that%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20I%20did%20enough%20of%20it%20where%20I%20was%20controlled%20and%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20a%20possession%20or%20a%20prize%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20it.%20And%20I%20will%20not%20do%20it%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the