't%20always%20questioned%20the%20grind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20moved%20from%20India%20to%20Singapore%20in%202013%2C%20when%20the%20IT%20company%20he%20worked%20for%20opened%20a%20local%20office.%20After%20changing%20jobs%20a%20few%20times%2C%20he%20cofounded%20a%20small%20IT%20services%20startup%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20originally%20planned%20to%20build%20the%20company%2C%20sell%20it%2C%20and%20cash%20out.%20But%20as%20the%20years%20passed%2C%20the%20finish%20line%20felt%20increasingly%20distant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%2C%20this%20is%20looking%20like%20several%20years%20away%20still%2C%20and%20I%20will%20have%20to%20work%20very%20hard%20to%20make%20it%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%2C%20now%2053%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20our%20%3Cstrong%3ERetirement%3A%20Chiang%20Mai%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eseries%2C%20which%20follows%20people%20choosing%20to%20retire%20in%20northern%20Thailand%20for%20reasons%20ranging%20from%20affordability%20to%20lifestyle%20and%20care.%20Next%20up%3A%20a%20look%20inside%20a%20family-run%20aged%20care%20facility%20for%20expats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20taken%20a%20similar%20path%2C%20or%20are%20planning%20to%2C%20email%20this%20reporter%20at%20agoh%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20he%20was%20no%20longer%20sure%20the%20stress%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolopreneur-ai-agents-dont-need-to-hire-staff-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erunning%20his%20own%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20justified%20the%20reward.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20several%20real%20estate%20investments%20Jain%20had%20made%20in%20India%20appreciated%20significantly%2C%20giving%20him%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-early-with-enough-money-for-one-year-no-regrets-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinancial%20security%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20consider%20stepping%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20then%2C%20why%20am%20I%20wasting%20my%20years%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20he%20began%20researching%20where%20he%20might%20want%20to%20spend%20the%20next%20chapter%20of%20his%20life.%20He%20knew%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-back-to-india-get-work-us-visa-culture-shock-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ego%20back%20to%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224173%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20sitting%20on%20a%20couch%2C%20smiling%20for%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b22347a96e437d6eb82d43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223130%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurning%2050%20led%20him%20to%20rethink%20his%20priorities.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20where%20to%20retire%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20a%20friend%20encouraged%20him%20to%20check%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-florida-cop-moved-to-chiang-mai-thailand-cheaper-safer-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChiang%20Mai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20city%20in%20northern%20Thailand%20he'd%20never%20visited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20five%20days%20in%20the%20second-largest%20Thai%20city%20sold%20him%20on%20the%20idea%2C%20and%20he%20threw%20himself%20into%20research%20about%20retirement%20visas%20and%20living%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20October%202023%2C%20when%20his%20lease%20was%20up%20for%20renewal%2C%20he%20decided%20against%20staying%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20spent%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20visiting%20family%20and%20traveling%20around%20Asia.%20In%20February%202024%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-left-america-chiang-mai-remote-work-thailand-safer-slower-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earrived%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef60961f-c0d1-4a21-9e98-a5691f147e57%5C%22%3EA%20new%20base%20in%20northern%20Thailand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFebruary%20is%20often%20considered%20the%20start%20of%20the%20burning%20season%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-abroad-journey-us-thailand-disney-imagineers-chiang-mai-healthcare-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Chiang%20Mai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20farmers%20burn%20agricultural%20waste%20to%20clear%20their%20fields%2C%20often%20causing%20haze%20to%20drift%20into%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20landed%20here%20in%20the%20worst%20possible%20time%2C%20but%20I%20still%20loved%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225344%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room%20in%20an%20apartment%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b219cf4d65ec517529df25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJain%20arrived%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20in%20February%2C%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bburning%20season.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThailand%20offers%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-single-mom-california-bangkok-thailand-daughter-affordable-slow-lifestyle-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-stay%20visa%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Jain%20holds%20a%20retirement%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Thai%20government%20publishes%20overall%20foreign%20resident%20figures%2C%20it%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20release%20a%20regular%20public%20count%20of%20retirement%20visa%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20civil%20registration%20data%20shows%20that%20163%2C036%20foreigners%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20retirees%20%E2%80%94%20lived%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20in%202024%2C%20a%20level%20broadly%20comparable%20to%20a%20decade%20ago.%20That%20amounts%20to%20about%209%25%20of%20the%20province's%20roughly%201.8%20million%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20connected%20with%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20through%20Facebook%20and%20viewed%20several%20units%20before%20choosing%20his%20current%20one-bedroom%20condo%20near%20Nimman%2C%20a%20trendy%2C%20cosmopolitan%20neighborhood%20known%20for%20its%20caf%C3%A9%20scene%2C%20chic%20boutiques%2C%20and%20international%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERent%20is%2014%2C000%20Thai%20baht%2C%20or%20about%20%24425%2C%20each%20month.%20His%20apartment%20building%20comes%20with%20a%20pool%20and%20a%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225861%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bedroom%20in%20an%20apartment%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Thailand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b219cfa7a4f9df67ba3367%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223906%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20many%20expats%20retire%20in%20Chiang%20Mai%20for%20its%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20for%20someone%20like%20Jain%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20India%2C%20it's%20actually%20more%20expensive.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20says%20he%20tries%20to%20keep%20his%20monthly%20expenses%20between%2040%2C000%20and%2045%2C000%20Thai%20baht.%20In%20months%20when%20he%20travels%2C%20his%20expenses%20can%20reach%20around%2060%2C000%20Thai%20baht.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20from%20Western%20countries%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20a%20major%20attraction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20somebody%20from%20India%2C%20it's%20two%20or%20three%20times%20what%20I%20spent%20back%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Jain%20said%20his%20decision%20was%20driven%20more%20by%20lifestyle%20than%20money.%20He's%20grown%20comfortable%20with%20Chiang%20Mai's%20slower%20tempo%2C%20its%20sense%20of%20safety%2C%20and%20what%20he%20describes%20as%20a%20culture%20of%20respect%20and%20patience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pool.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b217b24d65ec517529def5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJain%20says%20he%20appreciates%20the%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%20in%20Chiang%20Mai.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20likes%20to%20avoid%20stress%2C%20right%3F%20I'm%20very%20happy%20not%20to%20have%20stress%20living%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3d3d244-e349-4d1a-81fc-0a8a2fd0099c%5C%22%3ELife%20after%20the%20grind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20slower%20rhythm%20now%20shapes%20his%20days%20as%20a%20retiree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20starts%20most%20mornings%20at%20the%20gym%2C%20then%20prepares%20a%20quick%20breakfast%20at%20home%20and%20does%20some%20household%20chores.%20Some%20afternoons%2C%20he%20plays%20golf%20at%20a%20nearby%20driving%20range.%20On%20other%20days%2C%20he%20joins%20a%20hiking%20group%20and%20heads%20out%20to%20explore%20waterfalls%20and%20trails%20around%20Chiang%20Mai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20on%20a%20hike%20in%20Thailand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b22212a7a4f9df67ba33a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJain%20enjoys%20hiking%2C%20playing%20golf%2C%20and%20going%20to%20the%20gym.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Arinjay%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20evenings%2C%20he%20enjoys%20going%20for%20walks%20at%20nearby%20Chiang%20Mai%20University%2C%20whose%20scenic%20campus%20is%20a%20popular%20spot%20not%20just%20for%20students%2C%20but%20also%20locals%20across%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20enjoys%20being%20around%20people%2C%20building%20deeper%20connections%20with%20