pps%20to%20see%20how%20they%20stack%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20each%20attempted%20to%20build%20an%20app%20on%20Cursor%2C%20Lovable%2C%20and%20Base44.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20same%20prompt%20on%20each%20system%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20far%20we%20could%20get.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20three%20writers%20have%20been%20handed%20a%20gift%20with%20seemingly%20infinite%20potential.%20A%20sparkling%20promise%2C%20from%20vibe%20coding%20startups%2C%20that%20we%20can%20build%20anything%20without%20understanding%20a%20word%20of%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGone%20are%20the%20days%2C%20these%20companies%20say%2C%20when%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteens-vibe-coding-family-hackathon-cursor-ai-building-apps-steps-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoding%20novices%20%3C%2Fa%3Eneeded%20to%20rely%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-tech-lead-promotion-vibecoding-tips-ai-products-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechie%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20troubleshoot%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20dozen%20firms%20have%20rolled%20out%20tools%20offering%20the%20ability%20to%20build%20apps%20in%20seconds.%20All%20you%20need%20is%20a%20good%20idea%20and%20the%20platforms'%20free%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-code-review-token-costs-developers-backlash-engineers-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoding%20credits%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20growing%20wave%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femergent-ceo-vibe-coding-bitcoin-moment-ai-boom-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evibe-coding%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20raising%20big%20money%2C%20questions%20are%20emerging%3A%20Are%20these%20tools%20meaningfully%20different%3F%20Is%20the%20market%20already%20crowded%3F%20And%20can%20this%20be%20a%20sustainable%20business%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tried%20three%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20Cursor%2C%20Lovable%2C%20and%20Base44%20%E2%80%94%20to%20find%20out%20what%20each%20platform%20really%20offers%20and%20where%20they%20fall%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20prompts%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225370%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lee%20Chong%20Ming.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4f67c732a024514713551%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224027%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChong%20Ming%20hard%20at%20work%20building%20a%20writing%20companion%20app.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20this%20experiment%20at%20different%20levels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-ai-tools-underperforming-ramp-tech-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eof%20proficiency.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChong%20Ming%20had%20coded%20an%20app%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-takeaways-weekend-class-build-apps-non-technical-people-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evibe-coding%20workshop%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Cheryl%2C%20self-taught%2C%20had%20experimented%20with%20five%20vibe-coding%20platforms%20and%20made%20three%20web%20apps.%20Aditi%20was%20a%20true%20beginner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20each%20set%20out%20to%20make%20an%20app.%20For%20Chong%20Ming%2C%20a%20writing%20companion%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20cute%20creature.%20For%20Cheryl%2C%20a%20newsroom%20dashboard%2C%20a%20lite%20version%20of%20Asana%20to%20keep%20her%20team's%20work%20organized.%20And%20for%20Aditi%2C%20an%20app%20that%20acted%20like%20a%20newsroom%20photo%20coach%2C%20to%20deem%20whether%20a%20photo%20was%20good%20to%20publish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFirst%20impressions%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20laptop%20screen%20showing%20vibe-coded%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4f424299090a8c09b66fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAditi's%20newsroom%20photo%20companion%20tool.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChong%20Ming%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20When%20I%20asked%20Base44%20to%20plan%20the%20app%2C%20it%20responded%20with%20a%20few%20questions%20to%20clarify%20my%20prompt%2C%20with%20cute%20emojis.%20The%20plan%20it%20generated%20wasn't%20as%20detailed%20as%20what%20I've%20seen%20from%20Cursor%2C%20but%20it%20was%20user-friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovable's%20plan%20was%20even%20simpler%2C%20pared%20down%20to%20a%20few%20bullet%20points.%20It%20was%20just%20as%20easy%20to%20use%20as%20Base44.%20Within%20minutes%2C%20it%20generated%20a%20web%20app%20similar%20to%20Base44's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor's%20interface%20seemed%20built%20for%20serious%20builders%20looking%20to%20ship%20real%20products.%20Its%20planning%20questions%20were%20more%20advanced%20and%20thoughtful%2C%20asking%20if%20I%20wanted%20an%20MVP%20build%20plan%2C%20a%20clickable%20prototype%2C%20or%20a%20full%20product%20spec%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20of%20distinctions%20a%20software%20engineer%20would%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheryl%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI've%20always%20been%20one%20for%20the%20rule%20of%20cool%2C%20and%20Cursor%20looked%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20cool%2C%20with%20its%20all-black%20dashboard.%20But%20there%20was%20some%20charm%20in%20logging%20onto%20Lovable%2C%20with%20its%20girlypop%2C%20pink-heavy%20interface%2C%20and%20Base44%20offered%20some%20cheerful%20vibes%20on%20its%20tangerine-colored%20interface%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBase44%20and%20Lovable%20felt%20more%20like%20signing%20into%20a%20website%20and%20conversing%20with%20a%20chatbot.%20With%20Cursor%20and%20its%20MacBook%20app%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20%3Cem%3Ehacking%20into%20the%20mainframe%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20with%20all%20its%20complicated%20scrolling%20lines%20of%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAditi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOff%20the%20bat%2C%20Cursor%20looked%20intimidating%2C%20and%20the%20option%20to%20sync%20GitHub%20when%20logging%20in%20made%20me%20think%20it%20wasn't%20a%20platform%20for%20a%20non-technical%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Base44%20and%20Lovable%20were%20friendly%20and%20reassuring%2C%20with%20their%20gentle%20prompts%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20will%20you%20build%20next%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BReady%20to%20build%2C%20Aditi%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELearning%20curve%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cheryl's%20laptop%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4f469732a02451471353b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECheryl's%20dashboard%20on%20Base44.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChong%20Ming%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBase44%20and%20Lovable%20were%20easy%20to%20use.%20The%20app%20plans%20were%20written%20in%20plain%20language%20for%20everyday%20users%2C%20and%20the%20interface%20was%20beginner-friendly.%20It%20was%20clear%20where%20to%20click%20if%20I%20needed%20help%20or%20wanted%20to%20tweak%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor%20was%20a%20different%20story.%20There%20were%20things%20I%20had%20to%20decipher%20on%20my%20own%2C%20like%20%26quot%3Bfrontend%20built%20with%20Next.js%2C%20React%2C%20and%20TypeScript.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheryl%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20never%20felt%20more%20like%20a%20dinosaur%20than%20when%20I%20first%20tried%20using%20Cursor.%20It%20was%20embarrassing%20having%20to%20look%20up%20basic%20terms%20to%20know%20what%20I%20was%20dealing%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Base44%20and%20Lovable%2C%20I%20consistently%20typed%20in%20plain%20English%20and%20made%20the%20app%20edits%20accordingly.%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20wizard%2C%20watching%20the%20app%20preview%20morph%20and%20shift%20into%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAditi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'd%20never%20tried%20vibe%20coding%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20AI%20for%20help%20understanding%20AI.%20I%20asked%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20me%20refine%20my%20initial%20prompt%20into%20something%20I%20could%20plonk%20into%20the%20vibe%20coding%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Lovable%20and%20Base44%2C%20the%20learning%20was%20intuitive%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20talking%20to%20ChatGPT.%20With%20Cursor%2C%20I%20was%20completely%20lost%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20where%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20it%20was%20time%20to%20build%20the%20apps%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225530%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cursor%20dashboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4f6b0732a024514713556%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224148%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECursor%20was%20the%20hardest%20to%20master.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChong%20Ming%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Base44%20built%20me%20a%20writing%20companion%20app%20with%20a%20cute%20egg.%20The%20layout%20felt%20bland%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20full-fledged%2C%20functional%20app%20created%20without%20using%20up%20all%20my%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovable's%20build%20was%20similar%20and%20didn't%20use%20all%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20platforms%20could%20generate%20the%20app%3B%20the%20main%20variation%20was%20in%20aesthetics.%20I%20did%20appreciate%20that%20Base44%20and%20Lovable%20let%20me%20edit%20the%20app%20directly%20in%20the%20interface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cursor%20build%20process%20wasn't%20as%20hands-off.%20Unlike%20Base44%20and%20Lovable%2C%20which%20ran%20start%20to%20finish%2C%20Cursor%20required%20me%20to%20approve%20commands%20and%20grant%20permissions%20to%20override%20folders%20on%20my%20computer.%20As%20it%20generated%20code%2C%20I%20could%20pause%20and%20review%20it%2C%20something%20that%20would%20likely%20appeal%20to%20developers%20who%20want%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheryl%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20best%20things%20in%20life%20are%20free%2C%20and%20vibe%20coding%20credits%20are%20one%20of%20them.%20On%20Base44%20and%20Lovable%2C%20both%20platforms%20make%20it%20clear%20to%20users%20that%20they're%20cooking%20with%20limited%20credits%2C%20and%20that's%20fair%20%E2%80%94%20compute%20is%20costly.%20The%20mileage%20on%20each%20platform%2C%20however%2C%20was%20slightly%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovable%20gave%20me%20good%20bones%20for%20the%20project%20up%20front%20and%20created%20something%20that%20was%2C%20aesthetically%20and%20functionally%2C%20closest%20to%20what%20I%20wanted.%20But%20it%20burned%20through%20more%20free%20credits%20than%20my%20Base44%20project%20did%2C%20and%20some%20things%20still%20weren't%20working%20in%20the%20web%20app.%20I%20was%20stuck%20waiting%20for%20new%20credits%20to%20drop%20before%20I%20could%20make%20tweaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBase44%20gave%20me%20something%20very%20close%20to%20a%20complete%20dashboard%2C%20but%20it%20lacked%20some%20key%20functionality%20%E2%80%94%20the%20option%20to%20delete%20tasks%2C%20or%20to%20drag%20and%20drop%20unscheduled%20tasks%20into%20the%20calendar%20frame.%20But%20that%20was%20ironed%20out%20within%20minutes%20with%20two%20additional%20message%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECursor's%20steeper%20learning%20curve%20and%20multi-step%20process%20made%20it%20far%20harder%20for%20me%20to%20work%20things%20out.%20After%2010%20minutes%20of%20Googling%2C%20I%20gave%20in%20and%20typed%20into%20the%20Cursor%20chat%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20confused.%20What%20do%20I%20do%20now%3F%20Give%20me%20a%20guide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20told%20to%20go%20to%20Supabase%20and%20make%20some%20adjustments%20to%20the%20settings%2C%20then%20try%20to%20ship%20it%20via%20a%20local%20server.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20I%20was%20coming%20up%20on%20half%20an%20hour%20of%20getting%20frustrated%20with%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAditi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20development%20process%20was%20smooth%20sailing%20with%20Lovable%20and%20Base44.%20With%20one%20initial%20prompt%20and%20two%20additional%20tweaks%2C%20both%20platforms%20gave%20me%20usable%20apps%20that%20I%20thought%20would%20be%20handy%20newsroom%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20tried%20Base44%20and%20felt%20childlike%20wonder%20when%20it%20produced%20a%20clean%2C%20minimalist%20interface%20that%20let%20me%20drag%20a%20photo%20in%20and%20judge%20its%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20initial%20merriment%20wore%20off%2C%20I%20started%20testing%20the%20features.%20One%20thing%20I%20had%20not%20realized%20was%20how%20specific%20my%20prompts%20needed%20to%20be%2C%20expecting%20it%20to%20anticipate%20my%20needs.%20For%20example%2C%20both%20platforms%20initially%20did%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20crop%20the%20image%20or%20adjust%20the%20framing%2C%20and%20instead%20automatically%20chose%20the%20subject%20for%20me.%20An%20easy%20second%20prompt%20brought%20the%20apps%20closer%20to%20my%20initial%20vision%20%E2%80%94%20although%20I%20quickly%20learned%20how%20to%20ration%20my%20prompts%20lest%20I%20run%20out%20of%20my%20daily%20free%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovable's%20interface%20had%20a%20neat%20little%20photo-scanning%20animation%20that%20I%20thought%20added%20visual%20interest%20to%20the%20otherwise%20simple%20interface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20for%20Cursor.%20I%20had%20to%20download%20the%20app%20on%20the%20MacBook%2C%20while%20the%20others%20could%20run%20in%20the%20browser.%20When%20I%20finally%20downloaded%20it%20and%20fed%20it%20my%20prompt%2C%20it%20ran%20lines%20of%20obscure%20code%2C%20asked%20for%20permissions%20to%20things%20I%20didn't%20understand%2C%20and%20made%20me%20lose%20motivation%20to%20build%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20eventually%20gave%20up%20on%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20work%2C%20but%20the%20app%20kept%20prodding%20me%20with%20pop-ups%20for%20permissions%20all%20day%20until%20I%20force-quit%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20stick%20to%20my%20beginner-friendly%20platforms%20until%20further%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20the%20platforms%20stack%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225151%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lee%20Chong%20Ming%2C%20Cheryl%20Teh%2C%20and%20Aditi%20Bharade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4f50548461c18d7be6393%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223967%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20experienced%20varying%20levels%20of%20success%20across%20platforms.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChong%20Ming%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Lovable%20and%20Base44%20delivered%20working%20apps%20and%20refinements%20fast%2C%20but%20the%20quality%20didn't%20match%20Cursor.%20Cursor%20broke%20down%20what%20it%20added%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emade%20changes%20in%20detail%2C%20even%20if%20some%20of%20the%20jargon%20flew%20over%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20refined%20the%20app%2C%20Cursor%20didn't%20just%20tweak%20surface-level%20things.%20It%20suggested%20enhancements%20such%20as%20adding%20extra%20animation%20frames%20or%20making%20the%20pet%20move%20faster.%20When%20I%20said%20I%20didn't%20want%20a%20simple%20egg%2C%20it%20flagged%20that%20a%20drawn%20mascot%20or%20pixel%20pet%20would%20require%20new%20assets%20%E2%80%94%20a%20level%20of%20clarity%20the%20others%20didn't%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%20Lovable%20and%20Base44%20suggested%20things%20like%20adding%20entrance%20animations%2C%20which%20felt%20more%20gimmicky%20than%20meaningful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20building%20something%20serious%2C%20I'd%20go%20with%20Cursor%2C%20even%20if%20it%20takes%20more%20time%20and%20effort%20to%20get%20up%20to%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheryl%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20both%20Lovable%20and%20Base44%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20build%20workable%20newsroom%20calendars%20and%20get%20them%20from%20first%20prompt%20to%20publishing%20within%2010%20minutes.%20Base44%20gave%20me%20a%20complete%2C%20fully%20functional%20project%20I%20could%20immediately%20use%20and%20share%20with%20my%20team%20%E2%80%94%20and%20within%20the%20free%20credit%20range%2C%20too.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20I%20used%20my%20new%20set%20of%20credits%20on%20Lovable%20to%20make%20final%20tweaks%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20publishable%20dashboard%20with%20all%20the%20functions%20I%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Cursor%2C%20however%2C%20I%20just%20couldn't%20figure%20out%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20wrong%20and%20why%20the%20code%20wasn't%20running%20as%20I%20intended.%20I%20never%20got%20my%20dashboard%20off%20the%20ground%20there.%20Cursor%3A%20It's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enot%20you%2C%20it's%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20nontechnical%20background%2C%20a%20clear%20vision%20for%20the%20app%20you%20want%20to%20build%2C%20but%20limited%20time%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20little%20more%20coding%2C%20a%20one-stop%20shop%20like%20Lovable%20and%20Base44%20would%20be%20more%20your%20speed.%20If%20you%20do%20have%20more%20coding%20know-how%2C%20Cursor%20will%20give%20you%20access%20and%20oversight%20over%20the%20coding%20process%20within%20its%20free%20credit%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAditi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20a%20colors-obsessed%2C%20minimalism-loving%2C%20non-technical%20person%20who%20just%20wants%20to%20build%20a%20simple%20app%2C%20here's%20my%20leaderboard%3A%20Lovable%2C%20Base44%2C%20Cursor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20market's%20flooded%20with%20options%2C%20so%20take%20your%20pick%20while%20companies%20are%20being%20generous%20with%20credits%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225385%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20laptops%20with%20different%20vibe%20coding%20platforms%20on%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4f877299090a8c09b6718%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224039%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECursor%2C%20Lovable%2C%20and%20Base44.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20apps%20we%2