20budget%20exceeding%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%2C%20will%20be%20split%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20more%20expansive%20narrative%2C%20mirroring%20the%20'Dhurandhar'%20model.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fafter-dhurandhar-2-the-revene-box-office-success-and-ramayana-ss-rajamoulis-varanasi-to-be-split-into-two-parts-reports%2Farticleshow%2F129837019.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Udaybir%20Sandhu%20on%20his%2010%20year%20grind%20before%20breakout%20role%20as%20Pinda%20in%20'Dhurandhar%202'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774579199000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129837255%2Cimgsize-97236.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fudaybir-sandhu-on-his-10-year-grind-before-landing-the-breakout-role-as-pinda-in-dhurandhar-2-the-revenge-itne-zyada-auditions-diye-na%2Farticleshow%2F129837255.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129837255.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUdaybir%20Sandhu%2C%20who%20plays%20Pinda%20in%20Dhurandhar%202%3A%20The%20Revenge%2C%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20talked-about%20actors%20from%20the%20film%20despite%20having%20only%20a%20few%20scenes.%20In%20a%20candid%20chat%2C%20the%20actor%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20ten-year-long%20journey%20in%20Bollywood%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20out%20as%20a%20model%20in%20Delhi%2C%20moving%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20giving%20countless%20auditions%20and%20working%20in%20ad%20films%20before%20finally%20landing%20a%20role%20that%20has%20put%20him%20on%20the%20map.%20He%20also%20spoke%20honestly%20about%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20for%20outsiders%20to%20break%20into%20the%20industry%2C%20saying%20that%20one%20simply%20has%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20small%20opening%20and%20make%20the%20most%20of%20it%20when%20it%20comes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fudaybir-sandhu-on-his-10-year-grind-before-landing-the-breakout-role-as-pinda-in-dhurandhar-2-the-revenge-itne-zyada-auditions-diye-na%2Farticleshow%2F129837255.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20months%20after%20his%20arrest%20in%20Venezuela%2C%20Nicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro%20still%20has%20a%20long%20road%20to%20his%20criminal%20trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sketch%20of%20Nicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro%20in%20court%20in%20New%20York.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c5eca24133f63e1c778de0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro%20in%20court%20in%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EJane%20Rosenberg%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro%20faces%20narco-terrorism%20charges%20in%20the%20US%20and%20awaits%20trial%20while%20legal%20fees%20remain%20unpaid.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20in%20Venezuela%20and%20brought%20to%20the%20US%20in%20early%20January%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMaduro's%20Thursday%20court%20hearing%20focused%20on%20how%20his%20defense%20lawyers%20will%20get%20paid.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEighty-two%20days%20after%20US%20military%20forces%20seized%20him%20and%20his%20wife%20from%20Caracas%2C%20Nicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro%2C%20the%20toppled%20president%20of%20Venezuela%2C%20walks%20into%20his%2026th-floor%20Manhattan%20courtroom%20for%20the%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20a%20long%20road%20to%20his%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Justice%20Department's%20narco-terrorism%20and%20weapons%20charges%20against%20Maduro%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Cilia%20Flores%2C%20still%20do%20not%20have%20a%20trial%20date.%20His%20attorney%20has%20said%20he%20expects%20%26quot%3Bvoluminous%26quot%3B%20motions%20challenging%20his%20seizure%20and%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20criminal%20case%20hasn't%20gotten%20to%20those%20issues%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThursday's%20hearing%20focuses%20on%20how%20those%20lawyers%20will%20get%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Venezuelan%20government%20has%20said%20it%20would%20pay%20for%20Maduro's%20and%20Flores's%20legal%20fees.%20But%20the%20payments%20are%20being%20held%20up%20by%20the%20US%20Treasury%20Department%2C%20which%20has%20not%20issued%20a%20waiver%20on%20the%20sanctions%20against%20Venezuela.%20Kyle%20Wirshba%2C%20the%20lead%20prosecutor%20in%20the%20case%2C%20said%20the%20payments%20were%20withheld%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bnational%20security%20and%20foreign%20policy%26quot%3B%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20appears%20to%20annoy%20US%20District%20Judge%20Alvin%20Hellerstein%2C%20the%2092-year-old%20judge%20overseeing%20the%20criminal%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeering%20through%20his%20large%2C%20round%20glasses%20that%20magnified%20his%20cheeks%2C%20he%20asks%20Wirshba%20how%20%E2%80%94%20when%20the%20Trump%20administration%20was%20doing%20business%20with%20Venezuela%20%E2%80%94%20Maduro%20and%20his%20wife%20could%20possibly%20present%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20security%26quot%3B%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defendant%20is%20here.%20Flores%20is%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Hellerstein%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20present%20no%20national%20security%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20their%20arrest%2C%20Maduro%20and%20Flores%20have%20been%20held%20in%20the%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center%2C%20the%20infamous%20Brooklyn%20jail%20that%20has%20also%20been%20the%20temporary%20home%20of%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%2C%20Luigi%20Mangione%2C%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20and%20Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20associate%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThursday's%20court%20hearing%2C%20across%20the%20East%20River%2C%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20begins%2040%20minutes%20late.%20Across%20the%20street%20from%20the%20courthouse%2C%20groups%20of%20pro-Maduro%20and%20anti-Maduro%20protesters%20shout%20at%20each%20other%20in%20front%20of%20a%20playground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Maduro%20walks%20into%20the%20courtroom%2C%20he%20has%20a%20bright%2C%20beaming%20smile%20on%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood%20morning!%26quot%3B%20he%20booms%2C%20wearing%20a%20jail%20outfit%20of%20a%20drab%20khaki%20smock%20over%20a%20bright%20orange%20shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shakes%20hands%20with%20his%20lead%20attorney%2C%20Barry%20Pollack%2C%20best%20known%20for%20representing%20Julian%20Assange.%20Then%20he%20turns%20to%20the%20journalists%20sitting%20on%20dark-wood%20benches%20in%20the%20audience%20and%20wishes%20them%20%26quot%3Bgood%20morning%26quot%3B%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlores%2C%20wearing%20the%20same%20outfit%2C%20plus%20a%20brown%20scrunchie%20holding%20back%20her%20blonde%20hair%2C%20says%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20sit%20at%20the%20defense%20table%2C%20they%20wear%20big%2C%20black%20headphones%20through%20which%20they%20hear%20the%20court%20proceedings%20translated%20into%20Spanish%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20Flores's%20attorney%20Mark%20Donnelly%20says%20%26quot%3BFirst%20Lady%20Maduro%26quot%3B%20needed%20an%20echocardiogram%20to%20evaluate%20an%20issue%20with%20her%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20titles%20to%20be%20used%20in%20this%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20says%2C%20before%20telling%20the%20lawyer%20to%20keep%20him%20informed%20if%20Flores%20didn't%20get%20the%20treatment%20she%20needed%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVenezuela's%20now-former%20first%20couple%20ended%20up%20in%20New%20York%20City%20to%20face%20an%20indictment%20brought%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20accuse%20them%20of%20participating%20in%20a%20decadeslong%20drug-trafficking%20conspiracy%20involving%20Colombian%20terrorist%20organizations%2C%20which%20enriched%20themselves%20and%20their%20family%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Venezuelan%20citizens.%20The%20charges%20include%20narco-terrorism%2C%20cocaine%20importation%2C%20and%20machine%20gun%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20after%20US%20forces%20captured%20the%20couple%20from%20a%20military%20fort%20in%20Caracas%20where%20they%20were%20staying%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20called%20Maduro%20an%20%26quot%3Billegitimate%20dictator%26quot%3B%20responsible%20for%20funneling%20%26quot%3Bcolossal%20amounts%20of%20deadly%20illicit%20drugs%26quot%3B%20into%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20%26quot%3Bnow%20face%20American%20justice%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Bcampaign%20of%20deadly%20narco-terrorism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20White%20House%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Trump%20called%20Maduro%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20dangerous%20man%20who%20has%20killed%20a%20lot%20of%20people%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20charges%20against%20him%20were%20for%20just%20%26quot%3Ba%20fraction%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20conduct%20%E2%80%94%20with%20more%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20cases%20are%20going%20to%20be%20brought%2C%20as%20you%20probably%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20today%20is%20not%20yet%20about%20the%20core%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWirshba%2C%20the%20prosecutor%2C%20argues%20that%20it%20would%20be%20inappropriate%20for%20OFAC%2C%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20that%20grants%20licenses%20for%20sanctions%20waivers%2C%20to%20allow%20Maduro%20and%20Flores%20to%20access%20the%20wealth%20of%20the%20nation%20they%20%26quot%3Bplundered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Wirshba%2C%20Maduro%20should%20have%20anticipated%20he%20could%20not%20have%20gotten%20the%20money%20from%20Venezuela%20to%20the%20US%20due%20to%20the%20sanctions%2C%20leading%20Hellerstein%20to%20remark%20upon%20the%20oddness%20of%20the%20Venezuelan%20president%20being%20captured%20from%20his%20nation%20and%20brought%20to%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20think%20he%20would%20be%20in%20this%20court%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20judge%20asks%20with%20a%20sarcastic%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHellerstein%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20overseen%20cases%20involving%20financial%20scammers%20like%20Charlie%20Javice%2C%20former%20Trump%20lawyer%20Michael%20Cohen%2C%20and%20the%209%2F11%20terror%20attacks%20in%20his%2028%20years%20on%20the%20bench%20%E2%80%94%20calls%20Maduro's%20case%20%26quot%3Bunique.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20have%20been%20other%20cases%20that%20addressed%20whether%20criminal%20defendants%20could%20use%20potentially%20%26quot%3Btainted%26quot%3B%20funds%20to%20pay%20their%20lawyers%2C%20all%20of%20those%20cases%20involved%20money%20that%20was%20already%20held%20in%20a%20US%20bank.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20Hellerstein%20says%2C%20Venezuela%20had%20already%20agreed%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20legal%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20criminal%20defendant%20can't%20afford%20their%20own%20lawyer%2C%20a%20judge%20can%20appoint%20one%20for%20them.%20But%20Hellerstein%20says%20the%20%26quot%3Binvestigative%20responsibilities%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20be%20required%20to%20defend%20the%20complex%20narco-terrorism%20case%20would%20overwhelm%20the%20resources%20of%20a%20publicly-funded%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20remains%20unclear%20what%20Hellerstein%20could%20do%20about%20it.%20Forcing%20OFAC%20to%20issue%20a%20waiver%20would%20require%20a%20separate%20lawsuit%20brought%20in%20a%20different%20court%2C%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20Wirshba%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20remedy%2C%20Pollack%20says%2C%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bdismiss%20the%20case%26quot%3B%20and%20let%20Maduro%20walk%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHellerstein%20initially%20pours%20cold%20water%20on%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20OFAC%20didn't%20soon%20change%20its%20position%2C%20he%20would%20consider%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20such%20a%20serious%20step%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20take%20it%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Hellerstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20one%20and%20a%20half%20hours%2C%20Hellerstein%20decides%20he%20would%20hold%20another%20hearing%2C%20at%20an%20unspecified%20later%20date%2C%20to%20determine%20what%20steps%20he%20should%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Maduro%20leaves%20the%20courtroom%2C%20he%20only%20glances%20back%20at%20the%20audience%20behind%20him.%20He%20shakes%20the%20hands%20of%20his%20attorneys%20and%20walks%20stiffly%20toward%20the%20door.%20Flores%20kisses%20her%20lawyer%2C%20Donnelly%2C%20on%20the%20cheek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%2C%20the%20protesters%20are%20leaving.%20As%20a%20man%20passes%20by%20the%20courthouse%2C%20he%20yells%3A%20%26quot%3BViva%20Maduro!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmonths-after-arrest-nicolas-maduro-has-long-road-criminal-trial-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774578943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c5eca24133f63e1c778de0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmonths-after-arrest-nicolas-maduro-has-long-road-criminal-trial-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20prosecutors%20press%20sweeping%20narco-terror%20allegations%2C%20the%20Nicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro%20proceedings%20are%20bogged%20down%20in%20a%20bitter%20dispute%20over%20legal%20fees.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busi