efused%20to%20bow%20to%20Hegseth's%20demands.%20It%20is%20not%20immediately%20clear%20if%20the%20Justice%20Department%20will%20appeal%20the%20decision.%20In%20the%20hours%20after%20talks%20with%20Anthropic%20fell%20apart%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-pentagon-deal-fallout-backlash-anthropic-altman-amodei-trump-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Pentagon%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20grateful%20to%20the%20court%20for%20moving%20swiftly%2C%20and%20pleased%20they%20agree%20Anthropic%20is%20likely%20to%20succeed%20on%20the%20merits%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Anthropic%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20case%20was%20necessary%20to%20protect%20Anthropic%2C%20our%20customers%2C%20and%20our%20partners%2C%20our%20focus%20remains%20on%20working%20productively%20with%20the%20government%20to%20ensure%20all%20Americans%20benefit%20from%20safe%2C%20reliable%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20the%20Pentagon%20and%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20court%20filings%2C%20Anthropic%20officials%20said%20the%20risk%20designation%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-sues-pentagon-lawsuit-supply-chain-risk-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejeopardize%3C%2Fa%3E%20potentially%20billions%20in%20revenue.%20If%20the%20injunction%20remains%2C%20Anthropic%20will%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20to%20do%20business%20with%20defense%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELin%20wrote%20in%20her%20decision%20that%20the%20injunction%20does%20not%20require%20the%20Defense%20Department%20to%20use%20Anthropic's%20products%20or%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20in%20tech%20are%20closely%20watching%20the%20California%20case%2C%20since%20it%20tests%20whether%20the%20federal%20government%20can%20use%20some%20of%20its%20most%20severe%20powers%20to%20fo