C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta%20is%20pushing%20employees%20to%20use%20AI%2C%20and%20this%20doc%20shows%20how%20much%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c4f8b7299090a8c09b671a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222662%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20is%20all%20in%20on%20AI.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20has%20set%20goals%20for%20some%20employees%20on%20how%20much%20they%20should%20use%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20include%20targets%20for%20using%20AI%20code%20assistants%2C%20agents%2C%20and%20other%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20the%20company%20to%20be%20%26quot%3BAI-native.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20wants%20Meta%20to%20be%20%26quot%3BAI-native.%26quot%3B%20An%20internal%20document%20shows%20one%20way%20the%20company's%20CEO%20plans%20to%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20set%20goals%20for%20how%20much%20some%20employees%20should%20use%20AI%20tools%20for%20tasks%20such%20as%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20employees%20created%20a%20document%20to%20collect%20information%20about%20these%20goals%20from%20across%20different%20organizations%2C%20according%20to%20a%20copy%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20It%20includes%20goals%20set%20late%20last%20year%20and%20for%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20are%20using%20various%20methods%20to%20motivate%20staff%20to%20use%20AI%2C%20such%20as%20tying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employee-ai-adoption-non-technical-software-engineer-performance-review-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20use%20to%20performance%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20gamifying%20AI%20use%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-tracks-employees-ai-use-creates-game-to-boost-adoption-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompetitive%20leaderboards%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20states%20that%20Meta's%20creation%20org%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20building%20and%20maintaining%20core%20creative%20experiences%2C%20set%20a%20goal%20for%20the%20first%20half%20of%202026%20that%2065%25%20of%20engineers%20are%20expected%20to%20write%20more%20than%2075%25%20of%20their%20committed%20code%20using%20AI.%20Committed%20code%20is%20code%20that%20has%20been%20saved%20and%20tracked%20in%20a%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20Scalable%20Machine%20Learning%20org%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20AI%20models%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20had%20a%20goal%20for%20February%202026%20to%20achieve%2050%25%20to%2080%25%20AI-assisted%20code%2C%20the%20document%20said.%20It%20cited%20a%20comment%20alongside%20this%20goal%20from%20a%20senior%20engineering%20manager%20that%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20tracking%20this%20via%20metrics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20also%20listed%20several%20companywide%20goals%20for%20Q4%202025%20for%20central%20products%20%E2%80%94%20a%20horizontal%20org%20spanning%20Messenger%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20other%20major%20products.%20One%20target%20is%20for%2080%25%20of%20mid%20to%20senior-level%20engineers%20to%20adopt%20AI%20tools%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-assistant-helps-employees-performance-reviews-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDevMate%2C%20Metamate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Google's%20Gemini%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20a%20note%20that%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20%26quot%3Btool%20adoption%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20the%20percentage%20of%20code%20written%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%2055%25%20of%20code%20changes%20from%20software%20engineers%20across%20the%20central%20product%20orgs%20should%20be%20%26quot%3BAgent-Assisted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20goals%20listed%20in%20the%20document%20are%20tied%20to%20performance%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20well-known%20that%20this%20is%20a%20priority%20and%20we're%20focused%20on%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20employees%20with%20their%20day-to-day%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20They%20said%20that%20Meta's%20performance%20program%20is%20focused%20on%20rewarding%20impact%20from%20AI%20tools%2C%20not%20just%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22966dd76d-4553-4280-86a3-a5f06fef2afb%5C%22%3EHere's%20a%20breakdown%20of%20Meta's%20goals%20in%20the%20memo%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompanywide%20Q4%202025%20Goals%20(Central%20Products)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E55%25%20of%20software%20engineers'%20code%20changes%20should%20be%20agent-assisted.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E80%25%20of%20mid%20to%20senior-level%20engineers%20should%20adopt%20general%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScalable%20ML%20Team%20Goal%20(Feb%202026)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETarget%3A%2050%25%20to%2080%25%20AI-assisted%20code.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreation%20Org%20H1%202026%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E65%25%20of%20engineers%20should%20write%20more%20than%2075%25%20of%20their%20committed%20code%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Note%3A%20Some%20technical%20terms%20have%20been%20rephrased%20for%20clarity)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227df83adf-a214-452f-ad7e-71b175ed8e7a%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg's%20AI%20odyssey%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20is%20aggressively%20trying%20to%20make%20Meta%20what%20he%20has%20called%20an%20%26quot%3BAI-native%26quot%3B%20company.%20Meta%20has%20started%20tying%20employee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu