0the%20skylight%202%20calendar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c5768e299090a8c09b6a92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20a%20busy%20working%20Mom%20of%20four%2C%20I%20was%20disorganized%20and%20stressed.%20Skylight%20helped%20streamline%20my%20routine%20%E2%80%94%20but%20my%20favorite%20features%20are%20locked%20behind%20a%20paywall.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20life%20sometimes%20feels%20like%20a%20chaotic%20blur.%20When%20does%20my%20son%20need%20to%20be%20at%20soccer%3F%20Is%20my%20daughter's%20field%20trip%20today%20or%20next%20week%3F%20When%20are%20grades%20due%20for%20the%20class%20I%20just%20finished%20teaching%3F%20And%2C%20every%20night%2C%20what's%20for%20dinner%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20scoured%20the%20internet%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-planners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20planners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Having%20a%20visual%20way%20to%20track%20everyone's%20schedules%20helped%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20enough.%20I%20tried%20Google%20Calendar%2C%20but%20my%20kids%20had%20no%20way%20to%20check%20their%20own%20schedules%2C%20which%20meant%20they%20were%20constantly%20asking%20me%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20that%20day.%20I%20was%20at%20a%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20I%20started%20seeing%20ads%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118311264xs-20%26h%3Db2609c2b8d78f69d92cd67fbde72f6b0548cbe6929c9b869a994debb8de9cc1c%26postID%3D69c548557a1e7b24a6e7ef94%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fskylight-calendar-2-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fmyskylight.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fskylight-calendar%25252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESkylight%20Calendar%202%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20up%20in%20my%20social%20media%20feed%2C%20the%20second%20installment%20of%20the%20viral%20digital%20calendar.%20The%20ads%20promised%20that%20Skylight%20would%20solve%20my%20problems%20and%20streamline%20my%20family's%20schedule.%20I%20also%20heard%20other%20parents%20give%20glowing%20reviews.%20Something%20had%20to%20change%2C%20so%20I%20gave%20it%20a%20shot.%20Despite%20my%20initial%20skepticism%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20%E2%80%94%20though%20you'll%20have%20to%20get%20the%20%2479%20premium%20subscription%20to%20access%20my%20favorite%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1ba1139-98a5-4ab7-9129-b028f780cfc3%5C%22%3EMy%20review%20of%20the%20Skylight%20Calendar%202%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217dbe20b-3eef-43ca-b6c5-16e39024dc56%5C%22%3EEven%20the%20least%20tech-savvy%20parents%20can%20navigate%20setup.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225165%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20box%20showing%20a%20Skylight%20calendar%20wiht%20a%20black%20screen%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BLet's%20take%20on%20the%20day.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c5570d299090a8c09b68d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223874%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Skylight%20Calendar%20serves%20as%20a%20family%20hub%2C%20with%20to-do%20lists%2C%20schedules%2C%20shopping%20lists%2C%20and%20chore%20charts.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20my%20Skylight%202%20was%20easy.%20To%20get%20started%2C%20I%20simply%20connected%20the%20device%20to%20WiFi%20and%20paired%20it%20with%20the%20Skylight%20app.%20I%20often%20get%20frustrated%20when%20setting%20up%20new%20tech%20and%20need%20to%20consult%20my%20kids%20for%20help%2C%20but%20setting%20up%20the%20Skylight%202%20was%20easy.%20After%20creating%20my%20account%2C%20Skylight%20generated%20a%20unique%20email%20that%20I%20use%20to%20access%20the%20calendar's%20features%2C%20like%20mass%20calendar%20imports.%20I%20also%20made%20a%20profile%20for%20each%20member%20of%20my%20family%20and%20assigned%20them%20a%20color%20for%20an%20easy%2C%20visual%20way%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20everyone's%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Skylight%202%20is%20an%20upgraded%20version%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118311264xs-20%26h%3Dafa2e2aac57426eae6a9f75151bd6198e679abb6be3c69799cc79d827180bea3%26postID%3D69c548557a1e7b24a6e7ef94%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fskylight-calendar-2-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSkylight-Calendar-Touchscreen-Interactive-Schedules%252Fdp%252FB0C9V811L6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20Skylight%20Calendar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20faster%20performance%2C%20magnetic%20frames%2C%20and%20a%20lightweight%20stand.%20All%20Skylight%20calendars%20can%20be%20displayed%20horizontally%20and%20vertically%20and%20have%20the%20same%20features.%20It's%20also%20possible%20to%20customize%20the%20Skylight's%20display%20to%20see%20entries%20displayed%20by%20day%2C%20week%2C%20month%2C%20or%20person.%20As%20a%20bonus%2C%20Skylight%20calendars%20can%20display%20photos%2C%20and%20I%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20getting%20some%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20family%20photos%20I%20have%20off%20my%20camera%20roll%20and%20displayed%20somewhere%20my%20family%20could%20enjoy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22007a8468-3f90-4065-9a51-71b0f9c760db%5C%22%3ESyncing%20calendars%20is%20quick%20and%20easy.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20display%20of%20a%20Skylight%20calendar%20showing%20a%20week's%20worth%20of%20events.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c563a948461c18d7be6643%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Skylight%202%20has%20mass%20imports%20and%20syncs%20to%20both%20Google%20and%20Apple%20calendars.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20most%20pressing%20problem%20was%20getting%20my%20calendar%20under%20control%2C%20I%20started%20by%20getting%20a%20handle%20on%20the%20Skylight's%20capabilities.%20The%20Skylight%202%20can%20sync%20with%20Google%2C%20Apple%2C%20Outlook%2C%20and%20Cozi%20calendars.%20I%20use%20a%20Google%20Calendar%2C%20and%20it%20was%20really%20easy%20to%20sync%20my%20calendar%20with%20Skylight%20by%20tapping%20a%20few%20buttons%20on%20the%20Skylight%20app.%20I%20selected%20two-way%20sync%20so%20items%20I%20add%20to%20my%20Google%20Calendar%20will%20appear%20on%20my%20Skylight%202%20and%20vice%20versa.%20Although%20I%20only%20use%20a%20Google%20calendar%2C%20Skylight%20can%20sync%20with%20multiple%20calendars%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20calendar%20feature%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20mass%20import%20items.%20Most%20parents%20know%20the%20pain%20of%20tediously%20entering%20school%20events%20and%20sports%20schedules%20into%20a%20calendar%20one%20by%20one.%20Not%20only%20is%20this%20time-consuming%2C%20but%20I%20always%20worry%20about%20inadvertently%20forgetting%20to%20log%20a%20day%20off%20or%20a%20playoff%20game.%20Skylight's%20Magic%20Import%2C%20available%20with%20a%20Skylight%20Plus%20subscription%2C%20takes%20care%20of%20that%20problem.%20Now%2C%20whenever%20I%20get%20an%20attachment%20or%20email%20with%20a%20list%20of%20dates%2C%20I%20simply%20forward%20the%20email%20to%20my%20unique%20Skylight%20email%20address.%20Then%2C%20the%20events%20appear%20on%20both%20my%20Skylight%202%20and%20Google%20Calendar.%20This%20feature%20alone%20has%20saved%20me%20hours.%20I%20really%20like%20that%20Skylight%20sends%20you%20an%20email%20confirming%20what%20it%20put%20on%20the%20calendar.%20If%20there%20are%20any%20problems%20%E2%80%94which%20there%20rarely%20are%20%E2%80%94I%20can%20fix%20them%20with%20a%20few%20taps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20unexpected%20feature%20is%20that%20the%20Skylight%202%20syncs%20with%20my%20Google%20Calendar%20to%20display%20more%20than%20just%20calendar%20entries.%20Shortly%20after%20setting%20up%20my%20Skylight%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20notification%20pop%20up%20that%20I%20should%20leave%20for%20my%20son's%20soccer%20practice%20earlier%20than%20I%20was%20planning%20because%20traffic%20was%20heavy.%20I%20would%20have%20missed%20this%20notification%20if%20I%20had%20not%20had%20a%20Skylight%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20my%20phone%20on%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20love%20that%20I%20can%20glance%20at%20my%20calendar%20anytime%20I%20am%20in%20my%20kitchen%20for%20a%20quick%20update%20on%20the%20day%20(or%20week)%20ahead.%20I%20feel%20so%20much%20calmer%20not%20having%20to%20constantly%20check%20my%20phone.%20Another%20bonus%20is%20that%20my%20kids%20can%20help%20keep%20track%20of%20their%20own%20activities.%20After%20just%20a%20few%20days%20of%20having%20a%20Skylight%202%2C%20my%20kids%20started%20checking%20the%20calendar%20themselves%20instead%20of%20constantly%20asking%20me%20when%20they%20had%20scheduled%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d464f81a-ddbb-4661-8278-d91d19ecda6c%5C%22%3EI%20love%20the%20meal%20planning%20and%20recipe%20assistance.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Skylight%20Calendar%20display%20showing%20a%20meal%20plan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c56481732a0245147137d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20uploaded%20digital%20and%20written%20recipes%20to%20my%20Skylight%202%2C%20and%20it%20automatically%20created%20a%20grocery%20list.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20proud%20of%20this%2C%20but%20I%20often%20let%20meal%20planning%20fall%20to%20the%20wayside.%20Thankfully%2C%20the%20Skylight%202%20comes%20loaded%20with%20several%20recipes%20for%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20dinner%2C%20and%20snacks.%20Not%20only%20can%20I%20schedule%20meals%20by%20tapping%20the%20Skylight's%20screen%20or%20using%20the%20app%2C%20but%20I%20can%20add%20the%20necessary%20ingredients%20to%20a%20shopping%20list%20as%20well.%20Any%20step%20I%20can%20save%20in%20planning%20meals%20greatly%20increases%20the%20chances%20that%20my%20kids%20will%20eat%20something%20other%20than%20frozen%20pizza%20for%20dinner%2C%20so%20I%20really%20appreciate%20the%20streamlined%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20more%20experienced%20using%20the%20Skylight%202%20for%20meal%20planning%2C%20I%20also%20started%20taking%20photos%20of%20recipes%20from%20cookbooks%20and%20handwritten%20recipes%20from%20grandma%20to%20import.%20I%20discovered%20that%20I%20can%20also%20find%20recipes%20from%20links%20I%20found%20for%20meals%20I%20thought%20my%20kids%20would%20enjoy.%20Once%20new%20recipes%20are%20in%20the%20Skylight%20ecosystem%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20schedule%20meals%20and%20create%20a%20shopping%20list%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20I%20added%20the%20meals%20to%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20unexpected%20feature%20of%20the%20Skylight%202%20is%20the%20%26quot%3BFridge%20Photo%26quot%3B%20feature.%20One%20night%2C%20when%20I%20was%20exhausted%20and%20couldn't%20decide%20what%20to%20make%20for%20dinner%2C%20I%20simply%20took%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20inside%20of%20my%20refrigerator%20from%20the%20Skylight%20app.%20Skylight%20analyzed%20what%20I%20had%20in%20my%20fridge%2C%20suggested%20making%20turkey%20wraps%20with%20the%20ingredients%20I%20had%20on%20hand%2C%20and%20generated%20a%20recipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20has%20been%20eating%20better%20since%20I%20started%20using%20my%20Skylight%202%2C%20although%20these%20features%20are%20only%20available%20with%20a%20subscription.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222502b335-1abf-4e29-8053-b96eada5306b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20kids%20can%20check%20off%20their%20chores%20and%20earn%20rewards.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screen%20showing%20a%20skylight%20chore%20chart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c5732d48461c18d7be671b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20have%20a%20chore%20chart%20for%20everyone%20in%20my%20family%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20set%20goals%20and%20rewards.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20youngest%20son%20has%20a%20hard%20time%20remembering%20everything%20he%20is%20supposed%20to%20do%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20Skylight%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20enter%20reminders%20for%20him%20each%20weekday.%20Now%2C%20when%20he%20comes%20home%20from%20school%2C%20he%20can%20check%20the%20Skylight%202%20and%20tick%20off%20his%20tasks.%20Using%20Skylight's%20reward%20system%2C%20my%20son%20earns%20a%20star%20each%20time%20he%20completes%20a%20task.%20Once%20he%20earns%20enough%20stars%2C%20he%20can%20redeem%20them%20for%20a%20reward%20I%20choose%2C%20which%20is%20also%20displayed%20on%20our%20Skylight.%20We%20have%20used%20all%20kinds%20of%20rewards%20from%20movie%20night%20to%20ordering%20pizza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssigning%20tasks%20is%20useful%20for%20kids%20of%20all%20ages.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20can%20assign%20my%20older%20kids%20the%20task%20of%20emptying%20out%20the%20dishwasher%2C%20taking%20out%20the%20trash%2C%20or%20cleaning%20their%20rooms.%20However%2C%20so%20far%2C%20only%20my%20youngest%20has%20been%20motivated%20by%20the%20possibility%20of%20getting%20rewards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252b7c7fc-f115-45dc-b70b-5ab862f64293%5C%22%3EIt%20keeps%20track%20of%20your%20to-do%20lists%2C%20too.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Skylight%202%20also%20lets%20you%20add%20lists%20by%20uploading%20a%20photo%20with%20a%20to-do%20item%2C%20taking%20a%20photo%20of%20a%20handwritten%20list%2C%20or%20speaking%20into%20the%20mic%20in%20the%20Skylight%20app.%20The%20app%20comes%20preloaded%20with%20entries%20for%20a%20grocery%20list%20and%20a%20to-do%20list%2C%20but%20users%20can%20add%20any%20type%20of%20list%20they%20would%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20experimenting%20with%20using%20Skylight's%20lists%2C%20I%20can%20see%20how%20it%20would%20be%20useful%20for%20some%20people.%20However%2C%20for%20met%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20stick%20to%20using%20a%20tasks%20app%20because%20I%20find%20it%20easier%20than%20having%20to%20navigate%20through%20the%20Skylight%20app%20to%20find%20my%20lists.%20Whereas%20with%20my%20Google%20Tasks%20app%20I%20can%20start%20entering%20items%20immediately%2C%20in%20the%20Skylight%20app%20I%20need%20to%20navigate%20through%20a%20few%20steps%20to%20reach%20the%20part%20of%20the%20app%20where%20lists%20are%20housed.%20It's%20not%20difficult%2C%20but%20it%20is%20more%20time-consuming%20than%20I%20would%20like.%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20I%20wanted%20my%20entire%20family%20to%20see%20my%20embarrassingly%20long%20and%20detailed%20to-do%20list%20on%20the%20Skylight%20display%20anyway.%20Nevertheless%2C%20because%20I%20have%20started%20using%20Skylight%20for%20meal%20planning%2C%20I%20use%20the%20app's%20integrated%20shopping%20list%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223adac868-6178-4614-82ee-acd8f9277f6d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Skylight%202%20isn't%20cheap.%20I%20was%20hesitant%20to%20make%20the%20initial%20investment%20in%20the%20digital%20calendar.%20However%2C%20after%20seeing%20how%20useful%20the%20Skylight%20has%20been%20to%20my%20family%2C%20I%20regret%20not%20taking%20the%20plunge%20sooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20downside%20to%20Skylight%20calendars%20is%20that%20some%20premium%20features%20require%20purchasing%20a%20%2479%20annual%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3D