3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaughter-studying-abroad-italy-mom-panicked-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estudying%20abroad%20in%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20no-brainer.%20My%20great-grandparents%20are%20from%20a%20tiny%20village%20just%20outside%20Modena%2C%20and%20I%20was%20curious%20about%20my%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomething%20that%20took%20me%20by%20surprise%2C%20though%2C%20was%20the%20realization%20that%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20semester%20ended%2C%20I%20lived%20and%20worked%20in%20Rome%20throughout%20my%20early%2020s.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US%20and%20became%20an%20Italian%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-chicago-from-portland-big-city-life-affordable-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20in%20Chicago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Italy%20still%20feels%20like%20my%20second%20home%3A%20I%20make%20a%20point%20to%20spend%20summers%20there%2C%20mainly%20so%20my%20daughter%20can%20bond%20with%20her%20nonna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20lucky%20as%20I%20am%20to%20visit%20Italy%20every%20year%2C%20I%20still%20wish%20I%20could%20go%20more%20often.%20Thankfully%2C%20I've%20discovered%20a%20handful%20of%20places%20across%20the%20US%20that%20capture%20the%20energy%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-region-in-italy-to-visit-from-frequent-traveler-basilicata-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efavorite%20Italian%20regions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20cities%20offer%20Americans%20a%20slice%20of%20Italian%20culture%2C%20minus%20the%20hourslong%20flight%20overseas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20help%20quench%20my%20insatiable%20thirst%20for%20Italy%20with%20soul-stirring%20food%2C%20wine%2C%20history%2C%20and%20charm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECatalina%20Island's%20hidden%20coves%20and%20crystalline%20waters%20feel%20like%20Capri.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20beach%20on%20Catalina%20Island%20in%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689624dbcfc04e97619b1b79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaption%20TK%3Cp%3Evesperstock%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELocated%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20southern%20California%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-weekend-trip-from-los-angeles-catalina-island-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECatalina%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20about%2022%20miles%20long.%20It's%20easily%20accessible%20via%20ferry%20service%2C%20which%20operates%20out%20of%20three%20ports%20near%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20visited%20Catalina%20Island%2C%20I%20was%20awed%20by%20the%20dramatic%20shorelines%2C%20crystal-clear%20waters%2C%20and%20hidden%20coves.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20back%20on%20Capri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hiked%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Garden%20to%20Sky%20trail%2C%20catching%20panoramic%20views%20that%20felt%20straight%20out%20of%20a%20Mediterranean%20postcard.%20Then%2C%20I%20soaked%20up%20the%20sunshine%20at%20Descanso%20Beach%20while%20sipping%20a%20chilled%20glass%20of%20prosecco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFlorida%20is%20home%20to%20Coral%20Gables%2C%20a%20city%20that%20always%20reminds%20me%20of%20Lake%20Como.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225547%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20home%20in%20Coral%20Gables%2C%20Florida.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68962dfdcfc04e97619b1cfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaption%3Cp%3ERAUL%20RODRIGUEZ%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20glamorous%20Mediterranean-style%20architecture%2C%20lush%20gardens%2C%20and%20waterfront%20estates%2C%20Coral%20Gables%20feels%20like%20Florida's%20answer%20to%20Italy's%20Lake%20Como.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Italian%20Renaissance-inspired%20Vizcaya%20Museum%20and%20Gardens%2C%20built%20in%20the%20early%201900s%2C%20reminds%20me%20of%20the%20grand%20villas%20that%20line%20Como's%20shores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20plan%20your%20own%20visit%2C%20don't%20forget%20to%20check%20out%20the%20Venetian%20Pool%20%E2%80%94%20this%20public%20swimming%20spot%20was%20carved%20from%20a%20coral%20rock%20quarry%2C%20and%20(true%20to%20its%20name)%20feels%20straight%20out%20of%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChicago%20and%20Milan%20are%20%26quot%3Bsister%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20why.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chicago%20downtown.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a33f17a17a8c5b40530686%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225399%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELucky-photographer%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20surprise%20to%20me%20that%20my%20hometown%20of%20Chicago%20and%20the%20metropolis%20of%20Milan%20are%20officially%20sister%20cities.%20Both%20feature%20vibrant%20street%20art%2C%20designer%20boutiques%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20unsurprisingly%2C%20maybe%20%E2%80%94%20delicious%20Italian%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20recommend%20that%20tourists%20plan%20a%20trip%20to%20coincide%20with%20the%20Randolph%20Street%20Market%2C%20a%20pop-up%20vintage%20extravaganza.%20You%20can%20also%20explore%20Chicago's%20dynamic%20mural%20scene%20with%20a%20street%20art%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Chicago's%20pizza%20is%20as%20hearty%20and%20rich%20as%20any%20slices%20you'd%20find%20in%20Italy.%20You%20can't%20leave%20my%20hometown%20without%20trying%20our%20legendary%20deep%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20classic%20experience%2C%20head%20to%20Giordano's.%20The%20stuffed%20pizza%20here%20is%20a%20masterpiece%20of%20cheese%20and%20sauce%20wrapped%20in%20a%20golden%20crust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESonoma%20bears%20an%20uncanny%20resemblance%20to%20Tuscany.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vineyard%20in%20Sonoma%20County%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6896328acfc04e97619b1dd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERobert_Ford%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20visited%20Sonoma%2C%20California%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20much%20it%20resembled%20the%20Tuscan%20countryside%2C%20from%20the%20golden%20hills%20to%20rustic%20farmhouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20found%20myself%20gathered%20around%20a%20long%20wooden%20table%20at%20Pedroncelli%20Winery%2C%20surrounded%20by%20laughter%2C%20clinking%20glasses%2C%20and%20the%20comforting%20scent%20of%20fresh%20herbs%20and%20olive%20oil%2C%20I%20felt%20wrapped%20in%20the%20same%20warmth%20and%20magic%20of%20the%20Italian%20countryside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20obvious%20similarity%2C%20though%2C%20is%20the%20locals'%20deep%20appreciation%20for%20wine.%20You%20can%20even%20immerse%20yourself%20in%20vineyard%20life%20by%20staying%20at%20one%20of%20the%20several%20wineries%20that%20offer%20accommodations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVenice%20Beach%20in%20California%20feels%20just%20like%20the%20Italian%20city%20of%20the%20same%20name.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20canal%20in%20Venice%20Beach%2C%20Los%20Angeles.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6896352c194a2d49b8ae454f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaption%3Cp%3EALEXANDRE%20F%20FAGUNDES%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVenice%20Beach's%20bohemian%20vibe%20and%20canals%20are%20an%20almost-perfect%20replica%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-visiting-venice-for-first-time-with-family-kids-italy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVenice%2C%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20in%201905%2C%20the%20canals%20of%20this%20coastal%20Los%20Angeles%20neighborhood%20were%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20those%20in%20Venice.%20Whenever%20I%20stroll%20along%20the%20picturesque%20bridges%20and%20waterfront%20homes%2C%20I%20%3Cem%3Ealmost%3C%2Fem%3E%20feel%20like%20I'm%20in%20Italy%20%E2%80%A6%20all%20that's%20missing%20are%20the%20gondolas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrankenmuth%2C%20Michigan%2C%20reminds%20me%20of%20the%20Italian%20Dolomites.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Frankenmuth%2C%20Michigan%20in%20winter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689637f5f748d8c055f72c2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaption%3Cp%3ET-I%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Michigan%20city's%20Alpine-style%20buildings%2C%20hearty%20cuisine%2C%20and%20cozy%20charm%20really%20resemble%20the%20Dolomites%20in%20northeastern%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoments%20like%20browsing%20handcrafted%20wooden%20ornaments%20at%20Bronner's%20Christmas%20Wonderland%20(the%20world's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-christmas-markets-us-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elargest%20Christmas%20store%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20enjoying%20a%20traditional%20Alpine%20feast%2C%20and%20setting%20off%20on%20a%20riverboat%20cruise%20on%20the%20Cass%20River%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20celebrating%20Natale%20%E2%80%94%20or%20Christmas%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20August%2018%2C%202025%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20updated%20on%20March%2026%2C%202026.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-cities-that-look-like-italy-dolomi