22Jamie%20Dimon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c5691548461c18d7be668d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223851%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJPMorgan%20Chase%20CEO%20Jamie%20Dimon.%20The%20bank%20recently%20rolled%20out%20new%20objectives%20for%20its%20software%20engineers%20to%20boost%20productivity%20and%20coding%20quality%20using%20AI.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJPMorgan%20software%20developers%20say%20the%20bank%20is%20raising%20its%20expectations%20for%20AI%20use.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInternal%20company%20communications%20reveal%20the%20bank's%20new%20AI%20targets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20updated%20objectives%20affect%20members%20of%20its%20global%20developer%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20Chase's%20message%20to%20its%20global%20armada%20of%20software%20developers%20is%20clear%3A%20embrace%20AI%20or%20risk%20falling%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20company%20documents%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%20and%20posted%20to%20JPMorgan's%20intranet%20for%20employees%20lay%20out%20a%20series%20of%20new%20expectations%20for%20the%20bank's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-ai-technologists-talent-hiring-boom-salaries-influence-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%20workforce%2C%20who%20comprise%20the%20majority%20of%20its%2065%2C000-person-strong%20Global%20Technology%20division.%20The%20newly%20listed%20objectives%2C%20published%20on%20the%20intranet%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20say%20all%20software%20and%20security%20engineers%20are%20expected%20to%20%26quot%3Bdrive%20excellence%26quot%3B%20by%20adopting%20AI%20and%20%26quot%3Bcontributing%20to%20initiatives%20that%20improve%20productivity%2C%20speed%2C%20scalability%2C%20and%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20document%20authored%20by%20the%20bank's%20human%20resources%20leaders%20laid%20out%20two%20core%20objectives%20for%20software%20engineers%3A%20step%20up%20their%20coding%20game%2C%20and%20start%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-juniors-may-manage-bots-execs-say-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eharnessing%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20save%20time%20and%20get%20more%20done.%20The%20new%20language%20about%20objectives%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20added%20automatically%20and%20will%20appear%20by%20the%20end%20of%20March%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20image%20of%20the%20document%20on%20the%20intranet%20showed%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reference%20to%20upcoming%20changes%20to%20employees'%20goals%20expected%20to%20take%20effect%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month.%20The%20firm%20also%20instructed%20workers%20to%20develop%20clear%20goals%20with%20their%20managers%20that%20align%20with%20the%20bank's%20new%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDemonstrate%20measurable%20improvement%20in%20code%20quality%2C%20speed%20and%20productivity%20through%20regular%20use%20of%20approved%20AI%20coding%20assist%20tools%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20team's%20overall%20efficiency%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20one%20goal%20written%20by%20HR.%20%26quot%3BEngage%20in%20identifying%2C%20implementing%20and%20optimizing%20AI-driven%20automation%20opportunities%20within%20technology%20lifecycle%20management%20(TLM)%20processes%20to%20drive%20efficiency%20and%20support%20capacity%20unlock%20initiatives%2C%20ensuring%20all%20enhancements%20leverage%20current%20technology%20assets%20before%20considering%20new%20solutions.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20spokeswoman%20for%20JPMorgan%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20is%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-tech-budget-ai-20-billion-jamie-dimon-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWall%20Street's%20biggest%20spenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20technology%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20with%20projected%20tech%20investments%20reaching%20roughly%20%2420%20billion%20in%202026%20%E2%80%94%20far%20exceeding%20peers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-ceo-david-solomon-ai-headcount-investment-spending-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Across%20corporate%20America%2C%20companies%20including%20Meta%20and%20Google%20have%20begun%20pushing%20employees%20to%20adopt%20AI%20tools%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20evaluating%20their%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20five%20engineers%20across%20the%20bank%20who%20said%20the%20push%20to%20adopt%20AI%20has%20been%20felt%20far%20and%20wide%20%E2%80%94%20in%20managerial%20conversations%2C%20in%20intranet%20posts%2C%20and%20through%20dashboards%20that%20display%20who's%20using%20certain%20AI%20tools%2C%20and%20who's%20not.%20They%20added%20that%20discussions%20about%20productivity%20and%20AI%20adoption%20have%20become%20more%20frequent%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20It%20all%20comes%20as%20developers%20get%20ready%20for%20a%20pilot%20of%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20Code%20to%20be%20rolled%20out%20as%20soon%20as%20April%2C%20said%20a%20longtime%20IT%20developer%20in%20the%20Global%20Technology%20group.%20Claude%20Code%20would%20be%20made%20available%20alongside%20the%20four%20other%20large%20language%20models%20coders%20are%20already%20using%3A%20two%20from%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20two%20from%20Anthropic's%20Claude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bda32a5-550a-432f-8f15-2a9cbb96de1e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Anxiety'%20among%20developers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20developers%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20they've%20been%20encouraged%20to%20use%20AI%20tools%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20tasks%2C%20from%20writing%20code%20to%20preparing%20presentations.%20One%20dashboard%20that%20tracked%20adoption%20and%20usage%20of%20the%20bank's%20GitHub%20Copilot%20appeared%20to%20show%20details%20as%20granular%20as%20which%20employees%20had%20installed%20it%20and%20identified%20individuals%20as%20%26quot%3Blight%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bheavy%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bnon%26quot%3B%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20the%20message%20has%20added%20pressure%20inside%20a%20firm%20that%20has%20drawn%20scrutiny%20in%20recent%20years%20for%20its%20use%20of%20internal%20monitoring%20tools%20and%20performance%20tracking.%20Business%20Insider%20published%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-chase-is-tracking-zoom-calls-workplace-activity-using-wadu-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20series%20of%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20firm's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-jpmorgan-tracks-employees-zoom-calls-id-swipes-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWorkforce%20Activity%20Data%20Utility%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20a%20program%20that%20collected%20data%20points%20about%20how%20employees%20were%20spending%20their%20day%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20length%20of%20video%20calls%20to%20how%20long%20they%20spent%20drafting%20emails%20to%20where%20they%20were%20sitting%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety%20in%20the%20environment%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20longtime%20IT%20developer%20said.%20Those%20who%20don't%20use%20AI%20risk%20being%20seen%20as%20underperforming%2C%20the%20developer%20said.%20Another%20developer%20said%20their%20manager%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20meeting%20that%20availability%20of%20the%20new%20AI%20tools%20comes%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bexpectation%26quot%3B%20that%20velocity%20and%20output%20should%20show%20%26quot%3Ba%20noticeable%20increase%26quot%3B%20quarter%20over%20quarter.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThree%20of%20the%20five%20developers%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20the%20tools%20are%20helpful%2C%20despite%20discomfort%20over%20the%20tracking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de456af9-a0b2-47ea-97da-87c3163cb55e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20performance%20dimensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20updated%20guidance%20on%20AI%20use%20comes%20as%20the%20bank%20implements%20other%20adjustments%20to%20how%20it%20ranks%20workers'%20success%20on%20the%20job.%20Going%20forward%2C%20the%20bank%20said%20on%20the%20intranet%20portal%2C%20it's%20streamlining%20some%20of%20the%20primary%20%26quot%3Bdimensions%26quot%3B%20it%20uses%20to%20grade%20employees%2C%20pivoting%20to%20using%20two%20categories%3A%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20you%20achieve%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20business%20outcomes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%26quot%3Bhow%20you%20achieve%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20adherence%20to%20the%20firm's%20behavioral%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20screenshots%20from%20the%20bank's%20intranet%2C%20JPMorgan%20will%20segment%20workers%20into%20three%20buckets%3A%20%26quot%3Bstand%20out%26quot%3B%20for%20those%20who%20exceed%20job%20standards%2C%20%26quot%3Bachiever%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20employees%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bneeds%20improvement%26quot%3B%20for%20those%20who%20require%20%26quot%3Badditional%20support%26quot%3B%20and%20have%20struggled%20to%20perform%20consistently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20page%20Business%20Insider%20reviewed%20listed%20skills%20non-managers%20working%20in%20software%20engineering%20were%20expected%20to%20display%20across%20%26quot%3Ball%20performance%20dimensions.%26quot%3B%20One%20is%20%26quot%3BData%20Fluency%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%20the%20skill%20is%20applied%20by%20those%20who%20develop%20and%20drive%20%26quot%3Badoption%20of%20new%20tools%20or%20methodologies%20to%20leverage%20data%20in%20the%20flow%20of%20work.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BRate%20of%20adoption%26quot%3B%20is%20cited%20as%20one%20measurement%20of%20the%20employee's%20impact%20toward%20exhibiting%20the%20skill%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20from%20the%20JPMorgan%20intranet%20echo%20the%20firm's%20long-standing%20culture%20of%20internal%20monitoring%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-is-tracking-employee-id-b