icy%20chat%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsama%2Fstatus%2F1978129344598827128%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eerotica%20for%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20words%20%E2%80%94%20to%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20never%20happened%2C%20and%20now%20it%20looks%20like%20it%20never%20will%3A%20Altman's%20OpenAI%20has%20put%20those%20plans%20on%20hold%20%26quot%3Bindefinitely%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fde9bf0af-b241-424f-8229-5870b1c0d93d%3Fsyn-25a6b1a6%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20Altman's%20second%20big%20walkback%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20company%20canned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-discontinues-sora-video-app-amid-robotics-shift-compute-limitations-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESora%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20briefly%20popular%20video%20app%20it%20rolled%20out%20last%20fall.%20I've%20asked%20the%20company%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20retreats%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20new%20push%20at%20OpenAI%20to%20focus%20the%20company's%20efforts%20on%20things%20that%20could%20make%20money%20today%2C%20as%20it%20preps%20for%20an%20IPO%20at%20the%20same%20time%20it%20faces%20real%20competition%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20Google%20and%20Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20all%20this%20starting%20and%20stopping%20could%20be%20viewed%20as%20necessary%20growing%20pains%20at%20a%20fast-growing%20tech%20company%20%E2%80%94%20ones%20that%20won't%20mean%20anything%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20if%20it%20delivers%20on%20its%20world-changing%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20that%2C%20but%20Altman%20%3Cem%3Etold%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eus%3C%2Fem%3E%20we%20should%20expect%20this%20sort%20of%20stuff.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.samaltman.com%2Fsora-update-number-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlease%20expect%20a%20very%20high%20rate%20of%20change%20from%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20last%20fall%2C%20after%20hearing%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sora-mlk-pattern-apology-forgiveness-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtent%20owners%20who%20were%20outraged%20to%20find%20their%20stuff%20on%20Sora%20without%20their%20permission%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20make%20some%20good%20decisions%20and%20some%20missteps%2C%20but%20we%20will%20take%20feedback%20and%20try%20to%20fix%20the%20missteps%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20companies%20aren't%20allowed%20to%20make%20wrong%20turns%20and%20head%20up%20dead%20ends%20as%20they%20grow%20up%2C%20and%20even%20once%20they're%20fully%20mature.%20That%20kind%20of%20pivoting%20is%20celebrated%20in%20tech%20(and%20is%20why%20very%20few%20people%20are%20mad%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-mark-zuckerberg-metaverse-80-billion-loss-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20has%20stopped%20telling%20us%20the%20metaverse%20is%20the%20future%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-now-officially-owns-motorola-2012-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20once%20bought%20Motorola%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flenovo-to-buy-motorola-2014-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecided%20that%20was%20a%20bad%20idea%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20couple%20years%20later.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bmove%20fast%20and%20break%20things%26quot%3B%20lands%20differently%20when%20the%20company%20doing%20the%20moving%20and%20breaking%20isn't%20running%20a%20photo%20app%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-libra-flopped-before-crypto-boom-zuck-never-gives-up-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplaying%20around%20with%20crypto%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20OpenAI%20and%20its%20competitors%20say%20they're%20leading%20us%20into%20a%20world%20where%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20the%20way%20we%20live%20and%20work%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-economy-jobs-unemployment-citrini-disruption-openai-anthropic-2026-02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eor%20don't%20work%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ai-deal-sam-altman-pentagon-defense-department-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efight%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20everything%20else%20%E2%80%94%20will%20change%20in%20fundamental%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20investors%20have%20bought%20this%20pitch%2C%20which%20means%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-spending-race-capex-gdp-us-economy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20economy%20now%20seems%20yoked%20to%20all%20this%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20all%20of%20us%20are%20yoked%20to%20it%2C%20even%20if%20we%20never%20touch%20a%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20makes%20me%20slightly%20queasy%20to%20see%20Sam%20Altman%20promise%20dirty%20chats%20in%20October%2C%20and%20then%20walk%20away%20from%20the%20plan%20less%20than%20six%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20because%20dirty%20chat%20is%20obviously%20absurd.%20Lots%20of%20people%20in%20AI%20think%20romantic%20or%20sexual%20chatbot%20conversations%20are%20a%20real%20use%20case%20and%20could%20be%20a%20real%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20reasons%20it%20might%20be%20a%20bad%20idea%20for%20OpenAI%20were%20pretty%20obvious%20from%20the%20start.%20It's%20a%20giant%2C%20heavily%20scrutinized%20company%20that%20wants%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20central%20and%20indispensable%2C%20and%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc309y25prnlo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20going%20to%20get%20more%20scrutiny%3